MICHAEL: Dwight?

298
00:14:38,744 --> 00:14:41,008
Hey, David, how are you?
Michael.

299
00:14:41,080 --> 00:14:42,809
Good to see you.
Nice surprise.
Hey.

300
00:14:42,882 --> 00:14:43,871
Yeah.

301
00:14:43,949 --> 00:14:47,316
