319
00:15:46,478 --> 00:15:50,005
Hey, Dwight, great idea.
Dwight, Dwight, great idea.

320
00:15:51,483 --> 00:15:53,883
How'd you come up
with that idea?

321
00:15:55,020 --> 00:15:56,612
Inspiration.
Really?

322
00:15:56,689 --> 00:15:58,657
How were you inspired?
Never know
when it's going to strike.

323
00:15:58,724 --> 00:16:01,022
How did it pop
into your head, Dwight?
Just boom.

324
00:16:01,093 --> 00:16:02,651
Just give me the details
of how that happened.

325
00:16:02,728 --> 00:16:05,561
You're talking
to Dwight Schrute,
the biggest Wonka fan I know.

326
00:16:05,631 --> 00:16:07,622
