on the horn with the marketing
people in New York.

338
00:16:27,052 --> 00:16:28,542
DAVID: They should meet you.
DWIGHT: Great idea. Yeah.

339
00:16:28,620 --> 00:16:31,589
Pam, could you set up
a call in there
in about 15 minutes, please?

340
00:16:31,657 --> 00:16:33,522
Sure.
David. David.

341
00:16:33,592 --> 00:16:35,116
David. David.
DAVID: 'Cause I've got
this idea for a...

