of the meeting also?

343
00:16:37,129 --> 00:16:38,357
You probably have
too much to do around here.

344
00:16:38,430 --> 00:16:40,898
I don't want to
take up your time
with another meeting.

345
00:16:40,966 --> 00:16:43,526
Yeah, let's face it,
this meeting sounds like
it's Wonka fans only.

346
00:16:43,602 --> 00:16:44,660
He's never seen the movie.

347
00:16:44,737 --> 00:16:46,500
(DAVID LAUGHS)
All right.

348
00:16:46,905 --> 00:16:48,065
